On his return, his academic career went from strength to strength.

00:04:58.523 --> 00:05:03.083
He gave well-received lectures, won a position at his alma mater, Glasgow

00:05:03.083 --> 00:05:09.613
University, in 1751, and became the Head of Moral Philosophy a couple of years later.

00:05:10.673 --> 00:05:13.993
Importantly, moral philosophy, not economics.

